## Why This Is Asked
A hands-on end-to-end setup tests fundamental Azure services, governance, and secure delivery patterns in a beginner-friendly context.

## Key Concepts
- Static hosting on Blob Storage
- Azure Functions (Consumption)
- Cosmos DB SQL API
- Azure Front Door TLS/custom domain
- GitHub Actions CD
- ARM/Bicep templates
- Azure Policy tagging
- Cost management budgets
- CORS and API key basics

## Code Example
```javascript
module.exports = async function (context, req) {
  const key = (req.headers['x-api-key'] || req.query.api_key);
  if (key !== process.env.API_KEY) {
    context.res = { status: 401, body: 'Unauthorized' };
    return;
  }
  context.res = { status: 200, body: 'OK' };
}
