## Why This Is Asked
Tests practical understanding of identity-based security, secret management, and infrastructure as code in a beginner Azure context, with emphasis on environment isolation, governance, and CI/CD integration.

## Key Concepts
- Managed identities and Key Vault access policies
- Environment isolation with separate Key Vaults
- Tagging governance and policy enforcement
